sql: CREATE VIEW v0(c0, c1, c2) AS SELECT t0.c0, DATE '1969-12-11', (CASE ((DATE '1970-01-15') ::DATE) WHEN t0.rowid THEN '' ELSE t0.rowid END ) FROM t0 HAVING '0.5475091481997849' ORDER BY t0.rowid ASC, t0.c0, TIMESTAMP '1970-01-15 13:29:02' ASC LIMIT 596201550

CREATE VIEW v0(c0) AS SELECT (t0.c0 NOT IN ('|V],z\t)', (NULL IN (t0.c0, TIMESTAMP '1970-01-09 00:17:16', t0.rowid)), TIMESTAMP '1970-01-23 21:55:48')) FROM t0 GROUP BY ((NOT TIMESTAMP '1969-12-17 23:51:44') LIKE t0.c0 ESCAPE ((-427393590) COLLATE C)) ORDER BY ((+ t0.rowid) LIKE DATE '1970-01-01' ESCAPE 667349855) ASC, -1019281572 ASC, ((TIMESTAMP '1970-01-19 05:00:30')AND(t0.rowid)) LIMIT 693672335
